Margaret Nolan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margaret_Nolan 0 Margaret A. Nolan (born 29 October 1943) is an English visual artist, actress and former glamour model. She was born in Norton Radstock, Somerset to an English mother and Irish father, and grew up in Hampstead, London. Nolan was married to English playwright Tom Kempinski in 1967 and divorced in 1972.
